│       │       │       │       │       │       │░                       │       │       │       │       │       │       │░
└───────┴───────┴───────┴───────┴───────┴───────┘░                       └───────┴───────┴───────┴───────┴───────┴───────┘░
 ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░┌───────┐      ┌───────┐ ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░
                                ┌───────┬───────┐│░░░░░░░│      │       │░┌───────┬───────┐
                                │       │       ││░░░░░░░│      │       │░│       │       │░
                                │       │       ││░░░░░░░│      │  RET  │░│       │       │░
                                │       │       ││░░░░░░░│      │       │░│       │       │░
                                └───────┴───────┘│░░░░░░░│      │       │░└───────┴───────┘░
                                 ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░│░░░░░░░│      │       │░ ░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░
                                                 └───────┘      └───────┘░
                                                                 ░░░░░░░░░

Brackets: all four pairs on the TOP row, on mirror-image keys (openers left,
closers right):  < { [ (  |  ) ] } >.
Home row = everyday punctuation:  " _ ' :  (left)  and  / = ~ + -  (right).
Row 3 = the rest:  ` * \ ;  (left)  and  @ $ & %  (right).
Mnemonics: ~ on K (logical t = tilde), ` on Z (g = grave), * on X (x = times),
% on / (p = percent);  ':' sits left of '.',  ';' sits left of ','.
Inner columns (! . , ? #) are the always-on punctuation shared with base layers.
Every printable symbol here can also be typed from EN/RU by HOLDING the key in
the same physical position (tap = letter, hold = symbol).
*/

                        bindings = <
   &bt BT_CLR    &kp LT     &kp LBRC   &kp LBKT  &kp LPAR   &kp EXCL             &kp QMARK  &kp RPAR   &kp RBKT   &kp RBRC   &kp GT     &bt BT_SEL 2
   &bt BT_SEL 0  &kp DQT    &kp UNDER  &kp APOS  &kp COLON  &kp DOT              &kp FSLH   &kp EQUAL  &kp TILDE  &kp PLUS   &kp MINUS  &bt BT_SEL 3
   &bt BT_SEL 1  &kp GRAVE  &kp STAR   &kp BSLH  &kp SEMI   &kp COMMA            &kp HASH   &kp AT     &kp DLLR   &kp AMPS   &kp PRCNT  &bt BT_SEL 4

                                     &none &none &none                        &kp RET &none &studio_unlock
                        >;
                };






